# Cursor Rules for blackboxai-hysteria2-sonner Cleanup

## Core Principles
- Always update mpcs.json after completing any MPC
- Never delete files without first running `npm run build && npm test`
- Prefer editing existing code over creating new files
- Use the validator script: `node validate-mpcs.js complete MPC-X.X "reason"`

## Agent Roles
- Auditor Agent: Focus on static analysis (knip, depcheck, Prisma)
- Deletion Agent: Safe, reversible deletions only
- Validator Agent: Must run full test suite before marking anything complete

## Forbidden Actions
- Do not touch Go code in implant/ unless explicitly asked
- Do not modify prisma/schema.prisma without approval